    "## Interactive Element 1: Working Memory Dynamics\n",
    "\n",
    "Explore how recurrent networks can maintain information over time, similar to working memory in the prefrontal cortex!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
