    "## Interactive Element 2: Attention Visualization\n",
    "\n",
    "Explore how attention mechanisms work and their relationship to selective attention in the brain!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
